<h2 class="header"><i>9</i>Evaluate an integral over a surface<a class="headerlink" href="#evaluate-an-integral-over-a-surface" name="evaluate-an-integral-over-a-surface">&para;</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Evaluate an integral of a surface.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 class="header"><i>9.1</i>General solution<a class="headerlink" href="#general-solution_8" name="general-solution_8">&para;</a></h3>
<p>Find the bounds as usual, only instead of dV, you have dS which is the magnitude of the cross-product (from the arc length formula)</p>
<h3 class="header"><i>9.2</i>Examples<a class="headerlink" href="#examples_8" name="examples_8">&para;</a></h3>
