<h2 class="header"><i>10</i>Evaluate an integral over a region<a class="headerlink" href="#evaluate-an-integral-over-a-region" name="evaluate-an-integral-over-a-region">&para;</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Evaluate an integral over a region.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 class="header"><i>10.1</i>General solution<a class="headerlink" href="#general-solution_9" name="general-solution_9">&para;</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Might involve transforming to polar coordinates</li>
<li>Or, changing the order of integration</li>
<li>Or, transforming coordinates (don't forget the Jacobian)</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="header"><i>10.2</i>Examples<a class="headerlink" href="#examples_9" name="examples_9">&para;</a></h3>
